1. *Narodu* je potrebna pomoć. (The people need help.)
2. Kao narod, moramo biti ujedinjeni. (As a nation, we must be united.)
3. Vlast treba da služi narodu, a ne obratno. (The government should serve the people, not the other way around.)
4. Molim vas, *narode*, dajte podršku ovoj inicijativi. (Please, people, support this initiative.)
5. *Narod* se pobunio protiv režima. (The people revolted against the regime.)
6. Ovo je zemlja koja pripada svim njenim *narodima*. (This is a country that belongs to all its peoples.)
7. Poredak se mora održavati kako bi se zaštitio mir *naroda*. (Order must be maintained to protect the peace of the people.)
8. *Narodu* su obećane reforme, ali još uvijek nema nikakvih pomaka. (Reforms were promised to the people, but there have been no developments yet.)
9. Većina *naroda* podržava ovu politiku. (The majority of the people support this policy.)
10. *Narod* će uvijek tražiti slobodu i pravdu. (The people will always seek freedom and justice.)